headline: MetLife CFO to Speak at Raymond James 46th Annual Institutional Investors Conference
summary: NEW YORK, February 13, 2025--MetLife, Inc. (NYSE: MET) today announced that John McCallion, executive vice president and CFO, and head of MetLife Investment Management, will participate in a fireside chat at the Raymond James 46th Annual Institutional Investors Conference on Wednesday, March 5, 2025, beginning at 9:15 a.m. (ET).
